Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ovviamente ci siamo anche io,\N Ran e Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Abbiamo deciso di andare \Na svegliare Yumi Horikoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:15.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,rimasta chiusa in camera sua\N anche dopo la fine dei fuochi d'artificio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma una volta arrivati, abbiamo scoperto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:18.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,che si è suicidata sparandosi alla testa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:24.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Dopo aver controllato il suo cadavere, \Nsi è scoperto che è morta sette ore prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:28.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Quindi intorno alle 15:00, quando tutti \Nstavamo giocando a ping-pong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,prima di andare a vedere i fuochi.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.50,0:02:38.59,Titolo episodio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\blur3\bord0.1\3c&HB6D9E0&\pos(262.659,100.418)\c&HEBF8FE&\3a&H5E&}I{\c&HEBF8FE&}l{\c&HEBF8FE&} {\c&HECF8FE&}c{\c&HECF8FE&}a{\c&HECF8FE&}s{\c&HECF8FE&}o{\c&HEDF8FE&} {\c&HEDF9FE&}d{\c&HEDF9FE&}e{\c&HEDF9FE&}l{\c&HEDF9FE&}l{\c&HEEF9FE&}'{\c&HEEF9FE&}o{\c&HEEF9FE&}m{\c&HEEF9FE&}i{\c&HEFF9FE&}c{\c&HEFF9FE&}i{\c&HEFF9FE&}d{\c&HEFF9FE&}i{\c&HEFF9FE&}o{\c&HF0F9FE&} {\c&HF0F9FE&}a{\c&HF0F9FE&}l{\c&HF0FAFE&}l{\c&HF1FAFE&}a{\c&HF1FAFE&} {\c&HF1FAFE&}r{\c&HF1FAFE&}i{\c&HF1FAFE&}m{\c&HF2FAFE&}p{\c&HF2FAFE&}a{\c&HF2FAFD&}t{\c&HF2FAFD&}r{\c&HF3FAFD&}i{\c&HF3FAFD&}a{\c&HF3FAFD&}t{\c&HF3FAFD&}a\N{\c&HF3FAFD&} {\c&HF4FAFD&}d{\c&HF4FBFD&}i{\c&HF4FBFD&} {\c&HF4FBFD&}K{\c&HF5FBFD&}o{\c&HF5FBFD&}g{\c&HF5FBFD&}o{\c&HF5FBFD&}r{\c&HF5FBFD&}o{\c&HF6FBFD&} {\fs22\c&HF6FBFD&}({\c&HF6FBFD&}s{\c&HF6FBFD&}e{\c&HF7FBFD&}c{\c&HF7FBFD&}o{\c&HF7FBFD&}n{\c&HF7FBFD&}d{\c&HF7FCFD&}a{\c&HF8FCFD&} {\c&HF8FCFD&}p{\c&HF8FCFD&}a{\c&HF8FCFD&}r{\c&HF9FCFD&}t{\c&HF9FCFD&}e{\c&HF9FCFD&})
